callSkill(address,bytes).details: Calls external skill contracts that can modify this Aminal's state

params.data: Encoded parameters for the skill execution "Skills are the magic that transforms static digital beings  into dynamic entities capable of growth and evolution"
params.skillAddress: The address of the skill contract to execute

feed().details: Feeding increases both love and energy through bonding curves

returns._0: energyGained The amount of energy gained from this feeding "To feed an Aminal is to nourish its digital soul,  creating bonds that transcend the boundaries of code"

setAminalGenes(uint256,uint256[8]).details: Called when spawning new Aminals with specific traits

setBreedableWith(address,bool).details: Requires sufficient love to establish breeding consent

params.partner: The Aminal address to set breeding consent with
params.status: True to allow breeding, false to revoke consent "Love is the foundation of creation - only through mutual affection  can new digital life be brought into existence"

setDefaultGene(uint8,uint256).details: Used as fallback when Aminals don't have specific genes set

squeak(uint256).details: Uses love and energy to create a squeak - a digital cry of expression

params.amount: The intensity of the squeak (love and energy required) "When an Aminal squeaks, it speaks with the voice of its community,  channeling love into sound, energy into expression"

aminalIndex().notice: Unique identifier within the Aminal ecosystem

breedableWith(address).notice: Addresses this Aminal has consented to breed with

breeding().notice: Whether this Aminal is currently in breeding mode

dadAddress().notice: Address of the father Aminal (0x0 for genesis Aminals)

dataURI(uint256).notice: Given a token ID and seed, construct a base64 encoded data URI for an NFT.

defaultGenes(uint8).notice: Default Gene NFT IDs for each category (fallback traits)

energy().notice: Current energy level - the life force for actions

factory().notice: The factory that birthed this Aminal into existence

feed().notice: Feed this Aminal with love and energy

generateAttributesList(uint256).notice: Generate attributes list for NFT metadata

getAminalGene(uint256,uint8).notice: Get Gene NFT ID for an Aminal's trait category

lovePerUser(address).notice: Love saldo (given - used) by each user to this Aminal

loveVRGDA().notice: VRGDA instance for calculating love based on energy levels

momAddress().notice: Address of the mother Aminal (0x0 for genesis Aminals)

setBreedableWith(address,bool).notice: Set breeding consent with another Aminal

setDefaultGene(uint8,uint256).notice: Set default Gene NFT for a category
